==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: wetback
<hw>wet"back</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A Mexican who enters
the United States illegally, by wading across the Rio Grande; --
disparaging and offensive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>An offensive term for a
person of Mexican descent, usually intended and considered as an ethnic
slur.</def> <wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> greaser, taco.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wetbird</ent>⟦br⟧
